Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.71,0:00:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}June
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}SHOGI HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whose shoes are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're freaking enormous!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.09,0:00:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Kumakura 9th-Dan, right?\N- Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's here for the qualifier\Nfor the Kiryuu Championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what size is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want to check?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}RUMBLE RUMBLE RUMBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, 29.5 cm! Incredible, almost 30 cm!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how he kicked that hole in the inn's wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are beyond human!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.07,0:00:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fit these into a cubbyhole!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I was shocked, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For that cool, stone-faced Mr. Kumakura to kick\Nthe wall of an inn after losing a title match...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never realize he had so much hidden passion\Nbeneath that calm exterior.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:00:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That makes him so much more cooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to start kicking, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kengo, you the man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.10,0:01:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet if I put these on,\NI can become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.02,0:01:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get closer to Class A!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You might be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You could get closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Smith?\NYou think I can be Class A?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His feet are huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're unbalanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt\Nwhen you're having a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But can I have my shoes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.30,0:01:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a giant. So cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a professional shogi player's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true he's a 5th dan in judo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he was invited to join\Na mixed martial arts organization!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! It's already been 25 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our precious 50 minute lunch break\Nwill be over soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've only got time\Nfor the soba shop on the corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:45.93,DefaultLow2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikaidou Family Special\N30-Item Bland, Healthy Matsubana Bento
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}So we've both cleared our first match, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Newcomer Tournament\Nis for players 26 years old and younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}PLUMP
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}MOIST
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}LUXURIOUS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CHEW CHEW
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Players 5th dan and below can compete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CHEW CHEW
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are 42 players in the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CHEW CHEW
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NOM NOM
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're always eating healthy but high-class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should either eat or talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:21.63,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KIRIYAMA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:21.63,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NIKAIDOU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. If we win three more times,\Nwe'll reach the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You and I won't face off\Nat any rank-deciding competitions this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}FINALS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.31,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WIPE\NWIPE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The Legend Begins!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to hang in there, no matter what,\Nso we can battle each other in an official game!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"I need to hang in there"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you're pretty confident\Nabout getting to the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Where does that confidence come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Whatever you do, make it to the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's where our legend begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}PROJECT X\NTOP RUNNER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Meijin Nikaidou's Challenge\N~ The Rivals are Best Friends ~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After I become a Meijin,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get featured on a program like Project X,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:05:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and they'll show\Nblack-and-white freeze frames of that match!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikaidou thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}HEARTRENDING\NQUIVER\NQUIVER
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll have narration like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're getting way too deep\Ninto that future outlook of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And, are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Newcomer Tournament, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That brings back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a lot of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GASP
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But kid, you should only indulge in such\Nidle chatter after you beat this old man today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.12,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SMILE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A pie in the sky is tasty, but it won't fill you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.63,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SMILE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I'm looking forward to our game today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry we interrupted your lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He got mad at us because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From the gentle Arimoto 9th-Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GWARRR
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it,\Nit's all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Talking loudly about winning a title, becoming\Na Meijin, and going on NHK's Top Runner...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, you're always going with that\N"Oh, I'm not greedy" air,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,acting as if you're watching\Nwith the cool detachment of a spectator,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I know what's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About this Newcomer King, you're like,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Well, if I play properly,\NI can win it without much hassle."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where is that coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't need to make a fuss about the\NNewcomer King because of course I'll win it."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,regarding the age restriction,\NI'm totally confident,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but if I had to worry about anything,\NI think I'm getting closer to 6th dan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so if I don't win soon,\NI may miss my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll cross that bridge when I come to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of other title championships,\Nso I could always work hard for those."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's more or less what you're thinking\Ndeep in your heart, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Of course I don't think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Where do you come up\Nwith these ridiculous ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would never...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}BLUSH
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Kiriyama didn't realize it?\NThat brat pisses me off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Geez. That's adorable, though, dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}That's what I can't stand about a middle school\Nchild prodigy going professional.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Ticks me off. That idiot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Look at him blushing, the ninny.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}God help me, that's cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:08:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how puffed up you get with success,\Nand pretend to be a fake herbivore shogi player,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't abandon you over something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The reason is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who understands you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}(RIVALS)\NBEST FRIENDS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're best friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is so embarrassing! I'm the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! We're not done talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's so shaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A fragile teenager.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave him be, Nikaidou.\NIt's funnier this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief, Kiriyama. You don't have to worry,\Nsince this was always a den for demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll only find the strong-willed here,\Nas arrogant as a fiery soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Word of mouth is steadily driving up sales\Nof our "Puffy-Puffy Daruma."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're really starting to take root\Nas a March Town specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it's all thanks to you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've made Grandpa really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}BOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Let's get a specialty\Nin March Town
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so, would you help me\Nthink of an idea for a new sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This one will be a "summer confection," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something that looks refreshing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and would go well with cold, green tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Purr-purr...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have any dried bonito or dried sardines?\NI'd be satisfied with just a little.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you please pet me a little?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But when it comes to summer, our go-to\Nis the waterfront series that uses agar, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's important\Nto stick to the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would be perfect if we could\Nadd just a little novelty to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}SCRIBBLE\NSCRIBBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo, any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like, what would be fun\Nto see floating in the pond?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A duck?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ducks, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! That'd be cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's my granddaughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but if customers bought it as a souvenir,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the duck could fall off\Nwhile they are walking with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good point. As a gift, that shouldn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What if we sunk it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the block of agar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All of a sudden, it's become something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something... kind of sinister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo, any other ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like something that splashes into the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:44.64,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SCRIBBLE\NSCRIBBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does that bring anything to mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Splashes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,into the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A sandal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I dropped my sandal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll buy you new ones.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}(VISUAL IMAGE)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It dropped in there, huh? It's okay, it's okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A sandal, she says?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a child prodigy here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could this girl be a blessing\Nfrom the god of sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My granddaughter is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That sensibility is fresh and then some!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CRESCENT MOON
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will Crescent Moon be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, what are we\Ngoing to do with you, Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait. The bath's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You seem down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't forget the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the last one, so be sure to put it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nshe left some food on her plate tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hina...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I wonder if something happened at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,June
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ladybug Bush (Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EGG SALAD SANDWICH
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}FUJIMORI BAKERY
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:56.50,RightSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bought some\Nfor lunch, too
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:14:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The egg salad sandwich from\Nthe Fujimori Bakery on 2nd Street is delicious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're open from early in the morning,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so if you have a match, you could buy your\Nbreakfast there and eat it on the way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you, Sis!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fujimori Bakery?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rei, the doughnuts there are great!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Try them. You have to try them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you go there in the evening,\Nyou'll get them freshly-fried.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I should've gotten doughnuts, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like Hina recommended.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Then I could've had them\Nas a snack during the match.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}In today's open tournament,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}the amount of time the players have is short.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}It starts at 10,\Nso I can go in 15 minutes before that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I still have time, so I'll eat out here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:15:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I've played against today's opponent\Na number of times before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}He's good at playing quick games.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe he'll go with the Fujii System...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:08.99,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,COFFEE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case, it'll be a fast battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That bush...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. I remember.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There was one in the yard\Nof my elementary school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A ladybug bush.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Out of all the bushes there,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for some reason, ladybugs only laid\Ntheir eggs on that bush.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't seen one in a long time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It makes me feel nostalgic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nostalgic?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, that's not right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is... This feeling is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh! He's looking at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm scared!\N- Four-eyed robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who threw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}After I lost my parents and little sister\Nto a car accident,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I became part of\Na shogi-playing family in Tokyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My school in Nagano\Nwas small and I was alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But after coming to Tokyo,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I learned the true meaning\Nof being alone in my huge new school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, I'd never had a single friend before,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}KIRIYAMA THE SHOGI ROBOT
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so that was normal for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"It's normal."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what I tried to think.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SHOGI HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I went as far as to make myself unnoticeable\Nso the direct attacks on me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}from my classmates wouldn't escalate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was used to that kind of thing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I acted indifferent about it every day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}During recess,\NI would pretend to be absorbed in a book.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And for lunch break,\NI would stand out if I stayed in the room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I'd hide in the bushes\Nin a corner of the schoolyard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pass me the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rook to 2-3, promoted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}CHECKMATE IN FIVE MOVES\NTIME TRIAL
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Same, King.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bishop to 1-3, promoted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}King to 3-4.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My adoptive mother was kind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She always smiled with a worried expression.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I did everything I could think of\Nto please Mother, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash the rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have Rei do it?\NHe's better at it than I am, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Clean the bathtub?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should make Rei do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're always saying\Nthat he's such a good boy, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The more I helped around the house...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the more troubled Mother looked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Let's have a good game.\N- Let's have a good game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen, could you quit trying to be\Nso obvious about scoring points?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's our mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hate him. He's so creepy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's like a robot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}At night, I would get stressed, wondering if\Nthe rest of my life would be like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I couldn't even breathe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so I tried to become\Ncompletely absorbed in shogi,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I wouldn't have to\Nthink about anything else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the longest time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my days were like bobbing on a sea at night,\Nwith my legs failing to reach the bottom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I had that I can cling to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was this little board.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would solve every last one\Nof the composed shogi problems{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and read until I broke out into a fever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I moved on\Nto the untouched shogi game records{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in Father's study,\N50 years' worth of official matches.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From there, beautifully preserved shogi\Ngame records from the Edo era were stored.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I would study them day and night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd spend all of my days off at the Shogi Hall,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or playing shogi from morning to night\Nat a shogi dojo Father introduced me to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:21:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would play, and play, and play,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and play, and keep playing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would play, and play, and play,\Nand play, and play,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and play, and play, and play, and play and play.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Akari Kawamoto\NDinner\NCome over for\Ndinner tonight.\NWe're having\Nhamburger steak.\NAkari
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, that's how I'm here right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome. Oh, doughnuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.31,0:23:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bought them for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.73,0:23:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FUJIMORI BAKERY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.02,0:23:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're still a little warm. Freshly-fried, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GLEAM\NGLEAM
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.69,0:23:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I wanna eat doughnuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It would be nice to eat them\Nwhile they're still warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.16,0:23:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}But then we wouldn't have room for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina isn't home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.29,0:23:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? Can I partake?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it okay? Can I have some?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.01,0:23:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such long arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.30,0:23:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.72,0:23:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:24:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's wrong. Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.82,0:24:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.66,0:24:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.96,0:24:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.34,0:24:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.46,0:24:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ladybug Bush (Part 1)
