Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:38.06,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 26
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.55,0:24:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei brought over many books\Nabout beautiful Japanese-style sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.39,0:24:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
